On Escalation Ticket # 00430581 the new comment has been added: Robert Zavalczki:

I was able to reproduce this issue by installing the Browsec browser extension. The fix (that worked for me) was to add the port 1022 under the "Deep Packet Inspection Ports & Settings" / "Custom Ports" like in the screenshot found here: Screenshot 2025-01-16 at 17.15.44.png

The "traffic type" dropdown was set to "HTTPS".

FYI: @WaitingOnEngineer

[DevOps CommentId:11513554]
